---
title: Salisbury-Style Beef Fusilli with Mushrooms and Spinach
description: Halfway between the flavours of beef stroganoff and salisbury steak, this hearty pasta is full of savoury flavour. Drool-worthy creamy goodness guarantees this one will be a hit!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fusillis-au-boeuf-salisbury-8c0642b7.jpg
